TopicTitle: Eucl3d 3d ship prints @ SXSW Gaming Expo

Articles.Content:
The 3d models from Eucl3d are seriously awesome. [Check them out](https://tinyurl.com/ksae3d). http://twitch.tv/dasvaldez

Kerbal Space Academy had a booth at the SXSW Gaming Expo, and while we were helping people give KSP a try, Youtuber [Mikes Games](https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCl-g4uYdzrlCtd9AOhAUfEw) stopped by and shot this quick video.
